05:20.278 --> 05:22.864
Hey, you're doing pretty well.

05:22.947 --> 05:25.575
I think she'd be very proud.

05:27.535 --> 05:29.287
I hope so, 'cause, you know,

05:29.370 --> 05:31.998
everything I'm doing
is because of her--

05:32.081 --> 05:34.542
school, the paper, everything.

