Colin,

09:25.898 --> 09:28.651
what is this?

09:28.734 --> 09:32.822
{\an3}Oh, must be left over
from the holidays.

09:32.905 --> 09:34.532
Yeah, must be.

09:35.908 --> 09:38.327
Well, have a nice day.

09:38.411 --> 09:40.788
