Why don't you just go
to traffic school?

12:03.264 --> 12:04.181
It's no big deal.

12:04.265 --> 12:05.474
No luck.

12:05.558 --> 12:07.184
Silver's guy is out of business.

12:07.268 --> 12:08.978
Okay. So what's it going to be?

12:09.061 --> 12:11.981
We have traffic school
for Armenians,

12:12.064 --> 12:13.941
pizza lovers,
chocoholics.

12:14.024 --> 12:15.151
{\an3}Oh, here's
a good one.

12:15.234 --> 12:16.277
Gourmet traffic school.

12:16.360 --> 12:20.072
Ooh! We could watch gory movies
of traffic accidents

12:20.156 --> 12:21.657
