porcini mushrooms.

12:21.740 --> 12:23.451
How appetizing.

12:23.534 --> 12:25.453
Works for me. What do you think?

12:25.536 --> 12:26.454
I think we wouldn't
be in this mess

12:26.537 --> 12:27.830
if it hadn't been for you.

12:27.913 --> 12:28.998
Oh, don't blame me.

12:29.081 --> 12:30.958
You just couldn't
bear the thought

12:31.041 --> 12:33.002
