12:33.085 --> 12:34.670
(laughs)
You didn't.

12:34.753 --> 12:36.338
Well, that's not
what the cop said.

12:36.422 --> 12:38.007
{\an3}He said I was
winning. Remember?

12:38.090 --> 12:39.675
Wait. You asked the cop?

12:43.095 --> 12:46.015
You two are in a class
by yourselves.

12:46.098 --> 12:47.224
