13:04.325 --> 13:06.202
{\an1}You're kidding me,
aren't you?

13:06.285 --> 13:07.119
No. Not really.

13:07.203 --> 13:09.038
{\an3}I mean, the first time
I was ever in a limo

13:09.121 --> 13:11.874
was my... my high school prom.

13:11.957 --> 13:15.044
{\an6}My date practically
