the moon roof.

13:15.127 --> 13:17.546
That's very memorable.

13:17.630 --> 13:19.048
Yeah. That was
the good part.

13:19.131 --> 13:20.549
In the morning,
when I crawled home,

13:20.633 --> 13:22.676
