it was him.

13:26.639 --> 13:27.723
Who?

13:27.806 --> 13:30.851
My father.

13:30.935 --> 13:32.228
My real father.

13:32.311 --> 13:34.021
You never told me about him.

13:34.104 --> 13:38.025
Yeah. It's not a great
conversation starter.

13:38.108 --> 13:40.027
Well, what's he like?

13:40.110 --> 13:42.071
He's blind.

13:42.154 --> 13:44.240
He lost his sight in Vietnam.

13:44.323 --> 13:48.953
{\an6}Funny thing is,
he's a better artist
than I'll ever be.

13:49.036 --> 13:51.038
How's that
for poetic injustice?

13:51.121 --> 13:53.707
Why didn't you ever tell me
about him?

13:53.791 --> 13:55.292
I don't know.

13:55.376 --> 13:56.835
Never came up.

13:56.919 --> 13:59.380
{\an3}Who knows? You might
meet him someday.

13:59.463 --> 14:00.631
Hopefully, not.

14:00.714 --> 14:02.800
He's a pretty scary guy.

14:04.969 --> 14:08.430
So, how about you?

14:08.514 --> 14:11.058
{\an3}When was your first
time in a limo?

14:11.141 --> 14:14.311
{\an1}Oh, well, I was
practically born in one.

14:14.395 --> 14:16.105
{\an1}I was brought home
from the hospital in one.

14:16.188 --> 14:18.107
{\an1}I went to my first day
of school

14:18.190 --> 14:19.775
in one.

14:19.858 --> 14:21.318
Whenever my dad was in L.A.,

14:21.402 --> 14:24.446
he had a stretch
and a driver on payroll.

14:27.241 --> 14:31.662
But there's one thing
I've never done in a limo.

14:31.745 --> 14:33.831
No way. You're lying.

14:33.914 --> 14:35.332
You are lying.

14:35.416 --> 14:37.459
{\an1}Uh-uh.

14:38.919 --> 14:41.839
Well, there's a first
time for everything?

14:41.922 --> 14:42.965
Oh...

15:05.571 --> 15:07.990
So what traffic school did
you guys finally decide on?

15:08.073 --> 15:09.700
{\an1}Gourmet.

15:09.783 --> 15:11.201
Comedy-gourmet
traffic school.

15:11.285 --> 15:12.328
Very interesting.

